<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Carrossel de Cards</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #422040;
        }

        .carousel {
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1920px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .carousel-track {
            display: flex;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        .card {
        flex: 0 0 calc(30% - 20px); /* Ajuste das margens */
        max-width: calc(30% - 20px); /* Ajuste das margens */
        height: calc(25vw); /* Ajustando a altura proporcional */
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 2px solid #ec8d26;
        background-color: rgba(236, 141, 38, 0);
        margin-right: 20px; /* Ajuste das margens */
        box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .card h1, .card p {
            user-select: none;
        }

        .card h1 {
            padding: 70px 0 0 35px;
            font-family: "Raleway Bold", "Raleway", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #dfa5d9;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: normal;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .p-card {
            padding: 15px 25px 0 35px;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .card span {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-self: flex-end;
        }

        .span-box {
            justify-content: flex-start;
            padding-left: 35px;
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .span-box p {
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .card i {
            margin-top: 6px;
            margin-left: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .card a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ffd700;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1100px) and (max-width: 1300px) {
            .card h1 {
                font-size: 30px;
                padding-top: 60px;
            }

            .p-card {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .span-box p {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .card i {
                margin-top: 3px;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 900px) and (max-width: 1100px) {
            .card h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
                padding-top: 50px;
            }

            .p-card {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .span-box p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .card i {
                margin-top: 3px;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 700px) and (max-width: 900px) {
            .card h1 {
                font-size: 18px;
                padding-top: 30px;
            }

            .card {
                height: 250px;
            }

            .p-card {
                font-size: 14px;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .span-box p {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .card i {
                margin-top: 3px;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 500px) and (max-width: 700px) {
            .card h1 {
                font-size: 18px;
                padding-top: 50px;
            }

            .card {
                height: 250px;
                flex-basis: calc(45% - 10px); /* Aumentando o tamanho dos cards */    
                max-width: calc(45% - 10px);     
             }

            .p-card {
                font-size: 14px;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .span-box p {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .card i {
                margin-top: 3px;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 500px) {
            .card h1 {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding-top: 50px;
            }

            .card {
                height: 250px;
                flex-basis: calc(70% - 10px); /* Aumentando o tamanho dos cards */    
                max-width: calc(70% - 10px);     
             }

            .p-card {
                font-size: 14px;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .span-box p {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .card i {
                margin-top: 3px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-track">
            <div class="card">
                <h1>Stress</h1>
                <p class="p-card">Ansiedade, (TEPT), transtorno obsessivo compulsivo (TOC), fobias e síndrome do pânico.</p>
                <section class="espaco"></section>
                <section class="span-box">
                    <a href="#"><span><p>Ver mais</p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span></a>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h1>Humor</h1>
                <p class="p-card">Depressão, tristeza, apatia, euforia, isolamento, transtorno bipolar e outros transtornos do humor.</p>
                <section class="espaco"></section>
                <section class="span-box">
                    <a href="#"><span><p>Ver mais</p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span></a>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h1>Personalidade</h1>
                <p class="p-card">Borderline, paranoide, (TPD), esquizóide, antisocial, histriônica, anancástica e narcisista.</p>
                <section class="espaco"></section>
                <section class="span-box">
                    <a href="#"><span><p>Ver mais</p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span></a>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h1>Evolução Pessoal</h1>
                <p class="p-card">Insegurança, indecisão, auto cobrança excessiva, dificuldade de se expressar e instabilidade emocional.</p>
                <section class="espaco"></section>
                <section class="span-box">
                    <a href="#"><span><p>Ver mais</p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span></a>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h1>Título 5</h1> 
                <p class="p-card">Informação sobre o card 5.</p>
                <section class="espaco"></section>
                <section class="span-box">
                    <a href="#"><span><p>Ver mais</p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span></a>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h1>Título 6</h1>
                <p class="p-card">Informação sobre o card 6.</p>
                <section class="espaco"></section>
                <section class="span-box">
                    <a href="#"><span><p>Ver mais</p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span></a>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="../../public/js/carrosel-transtornos.js"></script>    
</body>
</html>

